game.name: Fancy Cars Hidden Stars
game.description:
Nothing could be better than exploring the games that feature top car models especially to those who love cars and hidden games! We have today brought to you a brand new arcade challenge where you have to find out the hidden stars to complete each level. Each level will come up with a new car picture and your job is to spot all the five stars that are hidden on different locations of that car image. 

Here the problem is that you would not have any hint button to use. But you would have only a magnifying glass to spot all the five hidden stars. Move it around the screen to get all of the five stars one by one and show off the world that you are the best finder of the hidden objects! You cannot move to the advanced level until you clear the present one in this fun hidden objects html5 game. Track how many stars you have spotted and how much is left by looking at the top of the screen!

This cool hidden object game features nice graphics, easy controls, seamless gameplay and an outstanding gaming environment. There is no time limit so you can take as much time as you want to find all the stars. Complete all levels to earn points and use them to unlock more and more fancy cars pictures in this new online hidden stars game! Check out our huge collection of free hidden games and meet the ones that can keep you busy for hours! You can see many other boys and girls games on our website and have fun with your friends, no download required.
